## R-SegBar Segmented Token Progress Bar — Implementation Review

### Criterion Assessment

| Spec Item | Status | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| Relay-D15 Composable interface | ✅ pass | `ProfessionSegment`, `TooltipBarEntry` types match spec. `PROFESSION_PALETTE` has all 8 professions + `_default`. Composable logic: filter >0, sort desc, color-map, percentage to 1 decimal. |
| Relay-D15 Component props | ✅ pass | `segments`, `totalBudget`, `totalUsed`, `tooltipEntries`, `warnThreshold`, `dangerThreshold` — correct types and defaults (0.7/0.9). |
| Relay-D15 Segment rendering | ✅ pass | Width proportional to `totalBudget`, min-width 2px, color from palette. Border-radius on first/last/only-child. |
| Relay-D15 Budget warning classes | ✅ pass | `budget-warn` at 70%, `budget-danger` at 90%, no class when under threshold or budget=0. |
| Relay-D15 Tooltip inline (per P4.2) | ✅ pass | No separate `AgentBreakdownTooltip.vue` — tooltip inlined per plan decision. Correct structure: title, rows with color dots + mini-bars + percentage, total row. |
| Relay-D15 Hover delays | ✅ pass | 80ms show delay, 150ms hide debounce. `onTooltipEnter` cancels hide timer. |
| Relay-D15 Accessibility | ✅ pass | `role="progressbar"`, `aria-valuenow`, `aria-valuemax`, `aria-label`. `role="tooltip"` on popover. `:focus-visible` outline. `focusin`/`focusout` mirror mouse. |
| Relay-D15 Animations | ✅ pass | Segment width 300ms ease-out, tooltip fade-in 150ms ease, fade-out 100ms ease. |
| Relay-D15 RelayView integration | ✅ pass | Old budget bar removed, `SegmentedProgressBar` in place. `useProfessionSegments` wired. `pieSlices`/`professionColors`/`cost-panel` all removed (zero search matches). |
| Relay-D15 CSS cleanup | ✅ pass | Comments at lines 811 and 1262 confirm removal of old budget-bar and cost-panel CSS. |

### Static Analysis

| Check | Status | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| Type signatures match spec | ✅ pass | All interfaces and function signatures conform to D15 |
| Error handling — division by zero | ✅ pass | `totalBudget > 0` check in `segmentStyle()`, `totalUsed \|\| 1` in composable |
| No dead code / unused imports | ✅ pass | All imports used, no unused variables |
| Timer cleanup | ✅ pass | `cancelTimers()` clears both timers on every enter/leave |
| Security (auth/data paths) | ⬜ n/a | Display-only component, no auth or data mutation |

### Compilation Check

| Check | Result |
|---|---|
| `npx vite build` | Pre-existing TS2307 errors in unrelated files (AutoDown editor, StreamingRenderer, etc.). **No new errors** from segmented bar code. |
| `vue-tsc` | Rollup MODULE_NOT_FOUND (linux-x64-gnu on WSL) — environment issue, not code issue. |

