### Overall Verdict: **approved_with_fixes**

Implementation code is high-quality and spec-conformant. Composable logic, component structure, CSS, accessibility, animation, and RelayView integration all pass review. **Blocking issue: zero test files exist.** The Coder must implement all 30 test cases (Relay-T23, T24, T26) before this feature can be marked verified.
